// ItemDrawer
// Slide-up bottom sheet for browsing and selecting session items on mobile.
// Supports search filtering, touch-drag-to-dismiss, and highlights the
// currently selected item.

Renders nothing when isOpen is false.

FUNCTION sortItems(items) -> Item[]
  Returns items sorted by lastModified descending (newest first).

---

FUNCTION filterItems(items, query) -> Item[]
  Returns all items if query is blank.
  Otherwise filters by case-insensitive substring match on item.name.

---

FUNCTION ItemDrawer(isOpen, onClose, items, selectedItemId, onItemSelect) -> JSX  EXPORT
  CALLS: ItemCard (ItemCard)
  Displays a backdrop overlay and a bottom sheet panel.
  Sheet contains: drag handle, search input, scrollable item list.
  Items are pre-sorted then filtered by searchQuery.

---

FUNCTION handleSearchChange(e) -> void
  Updates searchQuery, resets list scroll position to top.

---

FUNCTION handleItemSelect(item) -> void
  Calls onItemSelect(item) then closes the drawer.

---

FUNCTION handleBackdropClick() -> void
  Calls onClose.

---

FUNCTION handleSheetClick(e) -> void
  Stops propagation so clicks on the sheet do not hit the backdrop.

---

FUNCTION handleTouchStart(e) -> void
  Records the starting Y coordinate of a touch gesture.

---

FUNCTION handleTouchMove(e) -> void
  No-op; tracking is deferred to handleTouchEnd.

---

FUNCTION handleTouchEnd(e) -> void
  Computes deltaY from touchStart to touchEnd.
  IF dragged down more than 100px, calls onClose.
  Clears touchStart.
